      <title>哥伦比亚禁止向以色列出售煤炭，以结束加沙战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/colombia-to-ban-coal-sales-to-israel-to-seek-an-end-to-gaza-war</link>
